{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc3b61d22-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3904"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3904"},"text":"§ 3904.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Research and development","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3b61d23-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3904/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In carrying out medical and prosthetic research under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s7303"},"text":"section 7303 of this title","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary, through the Under Secretary for Health, shall provide for special emphasis on the research and development of adaptive equipment and adapted conveyances (including vans) meeting standards of safety and quality prescribed under subsection (d) of section 3903, including support for the production and distribution of devices and conveyances so developed."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3b61d24-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s3904/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In carrying out subsection (a) of this section, the Secretary, through the Under Secretary for Health, shall consult and cooperate with the Secretary of Health and Human Services and the Secretary of Education, in connection with programs carried out under section 204(b)(3) of the Rehabilitation Act of 1973 (relating to the establishment and support of Rehabilitation Engineering Research Centers).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc3b61d25-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/538/s5/a"},"text":"Pub. L